" tabs and windows {{{
nnoremap [tabwin] <Nop>
nmap     s [tabwin]
" tabpage changing
nnoremap          <C-TAB>       gt
nnoremap          <C-S-TAB>     gT
nnoremap          [tabwin]n     gt
nnoremap          [tabwin]p     gT
nnoremap <silent> [tabwin]t     :<C-u>tabnew<CR>
