nnoremap <silent> [tabwin]N     :<C-u>tabmove +1<CR>
nnoremap <silent> [tabwin]P     :<C-u>tabmove -1<CR>
" kill buffer
nnoremap <silent> [tabwin]d     :<C-u>bd<CR>
nnoremap <silent> [tabwin]D     :<C-u>bd!<CR>
